## Developer Guide

If you are new to using `nbdev` here are some useful pointers to get you
started.

### Install solveit_z2h in Development mode

``` sh
# make sure solveit_z2h package is installed in development mode
$ pip install -e .

# make changes under nbs/ directory
# ...

# compile to have changes apply to solveit_z2h
$ nbdev_prepare
```

## Usage

### Installation

Install latest from the GitHub
[repository](https://github.com/Rahuketu86/solveit_z2h):

``` sh
$ pip install git+https://github.com/Rahuketu86/solveit_z2h.git
```

or from [conda](https://anaconda.org/Rahuketu86/solveit_z2h)

``` sh
$ conda install -c Rahuketu86 solveit_z2h
```

or from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/solveit_z2h/)

``` sh
$ pip install solveit_z2h
```
